{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 48,
  "title": "第四十八章（無為）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "為學者日益 聞道者日損 損之又損 以至於無為 無為而無不為。"
    },
    {
      "text": "將欲取天下也 恆無事 及其有事也 不足以取天下"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "學謂政教禮樂之學也。日益者，情欲文飾日以益多。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道謂之自然之道也。日損者，情欲文飾日以消損。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "損情欲也。又損之，所以漸去。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當恬淡如嬰兒，無所造為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 23,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "情欲斷絕，德於道合，則無所不施，無所不為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "取，治也。治天下當以無事，不當以勞煩也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "及其好有事，則政教煩，民不安，故不足以治天下也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "務欲進其所能，益其所習。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "務欲反虛無也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有為則有所失，故無為乃無所不為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 30
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "動常因也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自己造也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "失統本也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
